               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡, Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>


                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="24v" facs="003">Fols 1r–24v</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ስላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ ሐዋዝ። እምነ፡ ከልበሌ፡ ወቈስጥ፡ ወእምነ፡ ሰንበልት፡ ምዑዝ።</incipit>
                    <note>Incomplete because of erasure to make room for the miniatures</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="25r" to="46r" facs="027">Fols 25r–46r</locus>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2839RepCh123">Malkǝʾa
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="omitted"/>በቋሉ፤ ወጽፉቅ፡ ጥቀ፡ ለአርዘ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ቈጽሉ። ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ካህናት፡ ዘላዕለ፡ ኵሉ።</incipit>
                    <note><locus target="#24v #36r" facs="027 038">Fols. 24v, 36r</locus> erased to make room for the picture</note>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="46r" to="59v" facs="048">Fols 46r–59v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ለዘኢየፈቅረኪ፡ እግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ውኩፈ፡ ኢይኩን፡ ጸሎቱ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                    <note>Missed text, <foreign xml:lang="ti">ዘተረስዓ፡ ናይ፡ መልአ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>, from the <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2891RepCh172">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Māryām</title>, the note is in Gǝ'ǝz and Tǝgrǝñña</note>
                  </msItem>

               </msContents>
